4Geeks Academy offers a course to become an AI Machine Learning Engineer, designed for beginners with no prior experience. This 16-week program teaches Python, SQL, and statistics, enabling students to build and deploy predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy. Classes, limited to 12 participants, are held three times weekly, and the course is available in English or Spanish. Graduates receive a recognized certificate. The program also emphasizes practical experience by tackling real-world data challenges.

